  "keyFeatures": [
    "Markup-aware linting that understands Markdown, AsciiDoc, reStructuredText, HTML, DITA, and more",
    "Highly extensible rule system via YAML — 12 built-in extension points",
    "Stand-alone binaries with no runtime dependencies (Go)",
    "Cross-platform: Windows, macOS, and Linux",
    "Custom vocabulary support (accept/reject word lists)",
    "Script-based rules using the Tengo scripting language",
    "Spelling checks with Hunspell dictionary support",
    "Package/style hub for sharing and reusing style guides",
    "JSON, line, and template output formats for CI integration",
    "Scoping system to target specific markup elements"
